# Commander Pairing Catalog

Last verified against Scryfall Oracle data: 2026-07-23

Rules authority: Wizards of the Coast *Magic: The Gathering Comprehensive Rules*, rules 702.124 and 903.

Runtime implementation: finite pairing families are embedded in every Deck Token as `PAIRING_CATALOG`. Each listed name is retrieved through the MTGR backend's exact `/card/[name]` endpoint and assembled locally into one native TTS deck. Search queries are not trusted to determine these pools.

