## Rules-derived dynamic pairings

- Standalone Partner uses the standalone-Partner query plus exact local ability validation.
- Partner with [name] uses the reciprocal exact card name from Oracle text.
- Choose a Background uses the full legendary Background roster.
- A Background selected first uses the full roster of commanders with Choose a Background.

## Safety checks

- The first Commander is removed from every exact catalog pool before requests begin.
- Selection is rejected when normalized names or Oracle IDs match.
- Every candidate is revalidated for the exact reciprocal ability.
- Doctors must have exactly the creature types `Time Lord Doctor`, with no additional creature type.

When Wizards adds or changes a finite pairing family, regenerate the affected list from Scryfall Oracle Cards and update both this document and `PAIRING_CATALOG`.
